  <brief_title>Perfusion Assessment of Wound Closure Techniques in Primary Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Wound Closure Techniques in Primary Total Knee Arthroplasty Using SPY Intra-operative Angiography</official_title>
